			<h4><a id="comment_link_64185215" name="comment_link_64185215" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23203691&amp;cid=64185215" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64185215)" >Re:A shocking amount of the web is machine generat</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64185215" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64185215); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~nightflameauto">nightflameauto</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~nightflameauto">( 6607976 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64185215">		
		on Wednesday January 24, 2024 @01:22PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23203691&amp;cid=64185215">#64185215</a>)
		<small> </small>
